{"tid":2354035,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"畫家警總案服刑完畢 今獲准就立法會案保釋","createTime":"2021-01-05T07:41:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-05T15:18:55.000Z","uid":240362,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"ab46a9a73f1e64b3fc399c984a1958e00967cfa0","tid":2354035,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T07:41:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12638\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F12638&d=QL2FFPepynYtbGyOTzoAG1I2fucNkJ94pdpDkYG0m8U%3D&h=7e597160\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12638</a><br />\n<br />\n#區域法院第廿七庭 <br />\n#高勁修首席區域法院法官 <br />\n#0701立法會 #提訊<br />\n<br />\nA6 畫家/潘(33)🛑已還押12日(服刑完畢的日子起計)<br />\n<br />\n（註：被告早前涉及 #0621警察總部 的一宗案件，後被判處監禁21個月。於2020年12月24日服刑完畢並交予懲教看管。該案之詳情請見蔽台紀錄。）<br />\n<br />\n控罪（只列出涉及A6的控罪）：<br />\n1.暴動 (所有被告)<br />\n2.進入或逗留在立法會會議廳範圍 (所有被告)<br />\n4.暴動 (A6)<br />\n5.非法集結 (A6)<br />\n6.刑事損壞 (A6)<br />\n<br />\n案情：<br />\n被控於2019年7月1日，在立法會綜合大樓，與眾被告及不知名人士參與暴動（控罪一）<br />\n被控於同日在立法會綜合大樓，違反《立法會（權力及特權）條例》第8(3)條所發出的行政指令，即在進入立法會會議廳範圍內，未有遵守立法會人員為維持秩序而發出的指示；A6另被控於同日在立法會外參與暴動（控罪二、四）<br />\n被控於同日在立法會大樓外及添美道2號政府總部外，連同其他身分不詳的人非法集結及被控於同日在立法會大樓外，無合法辯解而損壞屬於港府的立法會大樓；以及在政府總部外，無合法辯解而損壞屬於港府的政府總部外牆（控罪五、六）<br />\n<br />\n被告申請保釋獲批✅條件如下：<br />\n現金兩千元（某神父為擔保人）<br />\n宵禁2100-0700<br />\n不得離開香港，交出旅遊證件<br />\n居住在報稱地址（某院舍），接受院舍監管<br />\n一星期報到三次<br />\n不得直接/間接接觸控方證人<br />\n<br />\n案件押後至2021年3月26日1430區域法院再訊，期間被告以現有條件保釋。<br />\n<br />\n💛感謝臨時直播員💛"},{"pid":"9a2b748aafce943163229c4550c988f5611fe9e5","tid":2354035,"uid":50196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T07:42:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"306c6de15dc59c6ee8f50c8448df0bab5304cd82","tid":2354035,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T07:43:32.000Z","msg":"💛感謝臨時直播員💛<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2eadfd058373a10ad6c7a6cc083d1017892b277","tid":2354035,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T07:54:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"565cf157f5b9ba2664d4f449d293beca60c2c499","tid":2354035,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T07:55:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9fb645b47bdd2a99832bbc48af1e5956fa6d7f7","tid":2354035,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T08:11:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9dec4409b04645a55f05da337f2a579671f21b8","tid":2354035,"uid":301666,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T12:04:21.000Z","msg":"上月底刑滿　「畫家」潘浩超另一案被控暴動等 5 罪　獲准保釋<br />\n<br />\n報道：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3og1Oop\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3og1Oop&d=QL2FFPepynYtbGyOTzoAG1I2fucNkJ94pdpDkYG0m8U%3D&h=357d2e04\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3og1Oop</a><br />\n<br />\n前年 7 月 1 日，有示威者衝擊並闖進立法會大樓，多人事後被拘控，當中包括「佔旺畫家」潘浩超，他被控暴動等五罪，案件今於區域法院再提訊，並押後至 3 月 26 日再訊。辯方指潘就包圍警察總部案被判囚 21 個月，並於上月 24 日服刑完畢，今就被控暴動案申請保釋，法官高勁修經考慮後批准潘保釋，條件包括 2,000 元現金、由甘浩望神父自簽 2,000 元作人事擔保、不得離港、須居於長洲善樂舍並接受監管、每晚 9 時至翌晨 7 時宵禁、每周到指定警署報到 3 次等。<br />\n<br />\n潘浩超保釋步出區域法院，表示「<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">多謝所有人，終於脫離懲教嘅魔掌。我而家想去深水埗，想食文記車仔麵</span></strong></span>。」"},{"pid":"3c821fa5ccda66ab29a95fd3bf867cfbbfc710a5","tid":2354035,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T12:07:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b88469307da01940b63ee80a243218135178c9a6","tid":2354035,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T12:09:56.000Z","msg":"畫家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出名啲人啲老屈罪名真係唔會停<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c53b9d367f14010d9759ebbfc39f00188abc39e9","tid":2354035,"uid":36443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T12:12:03.000Z","msg":"畫家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aef180cc4ddf24fd1f68882fe0230df78ec868a","tid":2354035,"uid":74412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T12:28:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec8a0363a743e29a67e8edea7ece4905ccbabc6c","tid":2354035,"uid":61032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T12:30:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae773106788252859b49a4ec38085e77a71166f4","tid":2354035,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s